    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款 roguelike 骰子构筑游戏，你将化身为妖精林地归来的女王——格温妮薇儿捕猎反抗陷害亚瑟王的敌人，利用你的智慧策略以及运气释放强力攻击，击败敌人，并拯救出被施加魔法的亚瑟王！拯救陷入危机的卡美洛王国！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280790/extras/b7fe621c7749de1262d3ffa503375fee.avif?t=1752584157\" width=616 height=112 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将通过投掷骰子来积累点数，特殊点点数排布将激发出强大力量。通过多次投掷出合适的点数，你将逐渐积累力量打出数值巨大的伤害。但要小心，投掷的次数越多，风险也越大——只要有一次失败的投掷（Farkle），你将失去所有积攒的力量！愿王的圣剑给予你冒险的勇气，激发出你最强的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280790/extras/02141e2b0446b393b34827b0dcaf90a5.poster.avif?t=1752584157\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280790/extras/02141e2b0446b393b34827b0dcaf90a5.webm?t=1752584157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280790/extras/02141e2b0446b393b34827b0dcaf90a5.mp4?t=1752584157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280790/extras/37f0fd13d9cbba55b16a2bd41ab3b0a5.avif?t=1752584157\" width=616 height=112 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集并使用特殊能力的骰子，有 70+ 独特的骰子可以解锁新的能力，增强你的牌组。但这些特殊骰子并不是多多益善的，你需要思考什么样的特殊功能是你需要的，用你的智慧规划你的牌组，在策略与运气的双重考验下，找到最佳的骰子组合，战胜强敌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280790/extras/4ccf06b5dc837c306125f985426cb827.poster.avif?t=1752584157\" width=600 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280790/extras/4ccf06b5dc837c306125f985426cb827.webm?t=1752584157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280790/extras/4ccf06b5dc837c306125f985426cb827.mp4?t=1752584157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280790/extras/048f5d20297ddee74d4df59fcf8ed361.avif?t=1752584157\" width=616 height=112 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >叛乱的红眼骑士、成群的瘟疫之鼠、恐怖的噬魂鬼怪、神秘的疯狂巨人...对付超过 30 个凶恶的敌人，每一场冒险都充满谜题与挑战。用你的智慧与勇敢，战胜他们，解救被施展魔法的王，解救混乱中的王庭！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280790/extras/99b2c46178b57dfb44fa6a8a0acb6038.poster.avif?t=1752584157\" width=600 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280790/extras/99b2c46178b57dfb44fa6a8a0acb6038.webm?t=1752584157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280790/extras/99b2c46178b57dfb44fa6a8a0acb6038.mp4?t=1752584157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>来试试你的技能和运气，看看你是否有拯救王国的骰子！</strong></p>",
